Detailed Description

cvmx_zip_throttle

This register controls the maximum number of in-flight X2I data fetch transactions. Writing 0 to this register causes the ZIP module to temporarily suspend IOI accesses; it is not recommended for normal operation, but may be useful for diagnostics.
